I teamed up with my Wife & my 2 boys teamed with their cousins at a Laser Gun place.
We are winning until my smallest Boy ambushes us but I have him in my scopes & I'm about to shoot him & my Wife shoots me at point blank range. She says, "Sorry, but I can't k!ll my Son".

Women!

Did you see this episode? Where were you?
